  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow"><img src="/media/13103372/ski-in-ski-out-hero-900.jpg" alt="ChaletHero900" data-udi="umb://media/d790ce107ba9400d9a55b362b9034fc5" />
<p>Skiing and snowboarding holidays don't last forever, so you want to be able to make the most of every moment out on the slopes. Therefore, there is nothing better than ski-in ski-out accommodation.</p>
<p>Here at Inghams we have a selection of accommodation options in Chalets, Hotels and Apartments that offer the ski-in ski-out experience.  </p>
</div>
</div>
<h2>Ski-in ski-out chalets</h2>
<p style="text-align: left;">Chalets are a great accommodation option if you are looking for a home away from home stay but with a bit of luxury from our catered offering: Our team of friendly staff who will offer first class home-cooked food to making your beds after you rush out the door in the morning to make the most of the snow.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Here is a selection from our our ski-in ski-out chalets: </p>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow" style="text-align: left;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/d71c920311ae410ebf6c3d6d217d6cc2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d71c920311ae410ebf6c3d6d217d6cc2}" title="Chalet La Breche">Chalet La Brêche</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13103374/chalet-la-breche-838x450.jpg" alt="ChaletLaBreche" data-udi="umb://media/5dbec63174e445c8bba657d5e6436b61" /></p>
<ul>
<li><span>With modern wooden bath tubs or new showers, double basins and heated towel rails in the ensuite bathrooms.</span></li>
<li><span>An après-ski room on the lower ground floor with two infra-red saunas, a table tennis table and hot tub outside.</span></li>
<li><span>This resort has everything, no matter what your skiing ability, from wide open blues and greens to challenging black runs.</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/acff50eb9ad84862a464f68b551bc497" href="/{localLink:umb://document/acff50eb9ad84862a464f68b551bc497}" title="Alpe d'Huez" class="c-btn">Alpe d'Huez</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/2411c782bdc14ac48c17ef706cce6dc8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2411c782bdc14ac48c17ef706cce6dc8}" title="Chalet Marie">Chalet Marie</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13080794/photo-marc-b_renguer-036.jpg" alt="chaletmarie" data-udi="umb://media/9f5eb1c569a34c0bbc7b368e0b0643d8" /></p>
<ul>
<li><span>With high beamed ceilings, a feature fireplace, floor to ceiling picture windows and a balcony with great views across the resort.</span></li>
<li>A beautiful sun terrace with mountain views and a traditional sauna.</li>
<li><span>Very snow sure resort of Avoriaz is the highest in the huge </span><a data-udi="umb://document/a4e124db508748d6843732b7c10dd19d" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/france/portes-du-soleil-ski-area" title="Portes du Soleil Ski Area">Portes du Soleil</a><span> - the world's largest international linked ski area.</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/799f63184c52477c94171a057c16e540" href="/{localLink:umb://document/799f63184c52477c94171a057c16e540}" title="Avoriaz" class="c-btn">Avoriaz</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/b88f32b0e7684a67877821f675632f85" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b88f32b0e7684a67877821f675632f85}" title="Chalet La Rocheure">Chalet Rocheure</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13103373/chalet-rouchere-838x450.jpg" alt="ChaletRouchere" data-udi="umb://media/0c511c4f92f340eeb21c606cc0719e5a" /></p>
<ul>
<li><span>A beautifully renovated traditional farmhouse, full of charm but with a modern and stylish twist.</span></li>
<li><span>Though the propert is ski-in ski-out, there is a free shuttle bus the stops close to the chalet daily until 8pm if you want to head straight to higher lifts.</span></li>
<li><span>Selected as an Inghams Choice property with full chalet service, on-site sauna and can sleep up to 13 guests.</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d}" title="Val d'Isere" class="c-btn">Val d'Isere</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2>Ski-in ski-out hotels</h2>
<p>Hotels are the ideal option if you are looking for a great nights sleep after a busy day making the most of the resort. All our Hotel's offer fantastic rooms and great service, many with restaurants, spa facilities and cosy, log-fire bars. </p>
<p>Here is a selection from our our ski-in ski-out Hotels: </p>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/2034c79978494d81ba4c2622018d7288" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2034c79978494d81ba4c2622018d7288}" title="Hotel Piolets">Hotel Piolets</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13072722/hall-4.jpg" alt="HotelPiolets" data-udi="umb://media/5fc0da5df6804898b00dc2cc19cb66ee" /></p>
<ul>
<li>The hotel offers great spa facilities, including jaccuzzi and sauna. </li>
<li>All bedrooms are bright and spacious, mixing traditional materials with modern style.</li>
<li>The bar at the hotel is popular due to its panoramic views of the mountains. </li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/7bd0ea2aff2942389cbf8acdba0a0e77" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7bd0ea2aff2942389cbf8acdba0a0e77}" title="Soldeu" class="c-btn">Soldeu</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/061b256b6bff4767938b3743c3e5e06f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/061b256b6bff4767938b3743c3e5e06f}" title="Hotel Riml">Hotel Riml</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13080377/riml-bedroom.jpg" alt="hotelriml" data-udi="umb://media/c0200e5764624e548c071e1c779e9c85" /></p>
<ul>
<li>A special rooftop spa, where you can relax and take in the views.</li>
<li><span>Bedrooms are modern, comfortable and have pine décor, some of the rooms have balconies.</span></li>
<li><span>Great location, situated in the upper Ötztal Valley on the main Alpine ridge.</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/5c5a68def0234451a0e7113b85bac993" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5c5a68def0234451a0e7113b85bac993}" title="Hochgurgl">Hochgurgl</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/d22f6c8861554f7f94836e8506673e7a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d22f6c8861554f7f94836e8506673e7a}" title="Hotel Les Bergers">Hotel Les Bergers</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13103375/hotel-les-bergers-838x450.jpg" alt="HotelLaBergers" data-udi="umb://media/b6a7faef32844d5084cedeaadde980a1" /></p>
<ul>
<li>This hotel has been awarded with the Family Plus label so is ideal for families.</li>
<li>There are spa facilities at the hotel, including an adults only area.</li>
<li>This is also an Inghams Choice property, hand-selected by Inghams. </li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/acff50eb9ad84862a464f68b551bc497" href="/{localLink:umb://document/acff50eb9ad84862a464f68b551bc497}" title="Alpe d'Huez" class="c-btn">Alpe d'Huez</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Ski-in ski-out apartments</h2>
<p><span>Apartments are the best option when you want to make your ski or snowboarding holiday truly your own, at your own speed. With apartments of many sizes, you can cook your favourite meals, play games together in your own lounge space and make the most of the views surrounding you. </span></p>
<p><span>Here is a selection from our our ski-in ski-out apartments: </span></p>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/554f6c0643f6407f9cb55accaf1f97a7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/554f6c0643f6407f9cb55accaf1f97a7}" title="Residence Cheval Blanc Apartments">Cheval Blanc Apartments</a></h3>
<h3><img src="/media/13057185/france_val-thorens_residence_le_cheval_blanc_apartments_interior.jpg" alt="chevalblanc" data-udi="umb://media/299c7cc852bb479fb50b306a7ce237dc" /></h3>
<ul>
<li>An attractive set of apartments in a quiet area, with a delightful cocktail bar</li>
<li>Three Valleys <span> offers an unrivalled snow record and great skiing for all grades</span></li>
<li>Though these are self-catering apartments, you can have bread and pastries delivered each morning</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578" href="/{localLink:umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578}" title="Three Valleys Ski Area" class="c-btn">Three Valleys</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/2e5840735f6f4928a4933f3a2239957d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2e5840735f6f4928a4933f3a2239957d}" title="Residence Altaviva">Residence Altaviva</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13073096/altaviva-tignes-2.jpg" alt="ResidenceAltaviva" data-udi="umb://media/64d059ee94e046df93a83db7db6263e3" /></p>
<ul>
<li>A family favourite, with good sized apartments, welcoming public areas and close to town.</li>
<li>The apartments share a wellness area with a good sized pool.</li>
<li>There are kids Clubs on site for children up to 17 years of age.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" title="Tignes" class="c-btn">Tignes</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow" style="text-align: left;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/ba0513b2f2464b95829473d60d25bc50" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ba0513b2f2464b95829473d60d25bc50}" title="Arc 1950 Le Village Apartments">Arc 1950 Apartments</a><a data-udi="umb://document/ba0513b2f2464b95829473d60d25bc50" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ba0513b2f2464b95829473d60d25bc50}" title="Arc 1950 Le Village Apartments"></a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13103376/les-arcs-village-838x450.jpg" alt="LesArcs" data-udi="umb://media/ceab80f3d52345cab1528b3ac9ef4d13" /></p>
<ul>
<li>These are sought after, luxury apartments with well equipped facilities.</li>
<li>With access to the spa area, 24 hour reception service and apartments for up to 4 people.</li>
<li>A centralised location to the pedestrian village, with ski-in ski-out access.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/37e8bc9846b74cf1a001f969874ce05b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/37e8bc9846b74cf1a001f969874ce05b}" title="Paradiski Ski Area" class="c-btn">Paradiski</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p><a name="resorts"></a></p>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">The best ski-in ski-out resorts</h2>
<p><span>There are so many skiing and snowboarding resorts across Europe, we have selected just a few below that showcase some of the best ski-in ski-out accommodations so that you can make the most of your time out on the slopes and avoid the lengthy walks to lifts or travel time on buses. </span></p>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/1a5883a1530346a9ab78607d76c2e656" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1a5883a1530346a9ab78607d76c2e656}" title="Jungfrau Ski Region">Jungfrau, Switzerland</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13064201/switzerland_jungfrau-ski-region_mountain-top-skier.jpg" alt="swisski" data-udi="umb://media/9409228683104e4095c80b5caef2aea8" /></p>
<p><span>With some of the best terrain for skiing, snowboarding and snow activities - Switzerland overs the best range of winter activities </span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/37e8bc9846b74cf1a001f969874ce05b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/37e8bc9846b74cf1a001f969874ce05b}" title="Paradiski Ski Area">Paradiski, France</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13048597/where-le-paradiski.jpg" alt="franski" data-udi="umb://media/1e0cb0d7685e4d689e0ff719f4c3cbe5" /></p>
<p><span>Offering picturesque scenery, varied ski areas, plenty of resorts and charming traditional alpine villages, France never fails to tick all the right boxes</span><span></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/f5a15898b6694ef6a1c755346a0e1ba8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f5a15898b6694ef6a1c755346a0e1ba8}" title="Corvara &amp; Colfosco">Corvara &amp; Colfosco, Italy</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13092944/alta-badia_ski_by-andre-schoenherr-2.jpg" alt="corvita" data-udi="umb://media/e18a92a66dfe48dda4c5d663854bdaf4" /></p>
<p><span>Home to some of Europe's best skiing, scenery and food - skiing and snowboarding in Italy consistently impresses and is top of the list </span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/6063ab813f384ab795dc6aa1d337f576" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6063ab813f384ab795dc6aa1d337f576}" title="Obergurgl">Obergurgl, Austria</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13084758/obergurgl-town-shoot.jpg" alt="oberaus" data-udi="umb://media/4516057a993447e8853a398e18245b76" /></p>
<p><span>Austria celebrates its ‘Gemütlichkeit’ culture, which attempts to make guests feel homely and welcome - they are huge when it comes to Apres-ski</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2>Ski-in ski-out holiday FAQs</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>What does ski-in ski-out mean?</strong> - The slopes are right outside your door, so you don't need to walk to the nearest lift or slope, but ski and snowboarding straight away.</li>
<li><strong>Is ski-in ski-out worth doing?</strong> - The convenience is a very valid reason to opt for ski-in ski-out accommodation, as well as the fact you are making the most of your skiing time by literally skiing or snowboarding to and from your door. </li>
<li><strong>How do I know if the holiday I am booking is a ski-in ski-out option?</strong> - The accommodation page you are looking at should highlight this fact in it's introduction information, otherwise you will find this detail under the tabs section of the accommodations page. </li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Travel with confidence </h2>
<p>When you choose an Inghams holiday, you can travel with confidence. We’re here to take the stress out of travelling. We’ve put extra measures in place for your peace of mind. We’ll help keep both you and your money safe.</p>
<p><img src="/media/13095389/inghams-in-safe-hands-charcoal.png" alt="safehands" data-udi="umb://media/afba17a916e84fcc848acce5dda4f9c4" /></p>
<p> </p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<div class="c-card_content c-section u-margin-top u-margin-bottom u-margin-left u-margin-right">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">How to book your holiday</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Simply give us a call to book your holiday. Flights, hotel and transport? We’ve got you covered. </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call us to book today</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
